          img src="/images/takayama/green_tea/green_tea.jpg" data-1x="/images/takayama/green_tea/green_tea-1x.jpg" data-2x="/images/takayama/green_tea/green_tea-2x.jpg" alt="Green Tea Latte and Warm Waffles"
        ' Green Tea Latte and Warm Waffles
      p Takayama is a sake-brewing town and we were lucky to visit during the wintertime when they open the breweries for tours from January to February. We had a short tour of a brewery and were able to sample some sake and some warm sake porridge. 
